Thanks!

Deno version:
```
deno 1.2.1
v8 8.5.216
typescript 3.9.2
```

Example code:
```
Deno.compile("main.js", { "main.js": `
export class Foo {
  constructor() {
    console.log("foo");
  }
  export get() {
    console.log("bar");
